## ✅ Verification Commands

```ios
show ip nat translations              ! Active NAT/PAT table
show ip nat translations verbose      ! Detailed view with timers
show ip nat statistics                ! Hit counts, misses, pool usage
show running-config | include nat     ! Quick config review
clear ip nat translation *            ! Clear all dynamic translations
```

**Expected `show ip nat translations` output during PAT:**
```
Pro  Inside global     Inside local      Outside local    Outside global
tcp  203.0.113.1:1025  10.0.0.10:1025   8.8.8.8:80      8.8.8.8:80
tcp  203.0.113.1:1026  10.0.0.11:1025   8.8.8.8:80      8.8.8.8:80
tcp  203.0.113.1:1027  10.0.0.12:1025   8.8.8.8:80      8.8.8.8:80
```

All three PCs share `203.0.113.1` but use different source ports.

